Subject: [PATCH] selftests/resctrl: Extend signal handler coverage to unmount
 on receiving signal
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1012628
